profile: We are a locally owned and operated residential roofing company dedicated to providing the highest levels of quality service and workmanship to both contractors and homeowners in Vernon, Salmon Arm, Kamloops, Kelowna and the surrounding areas. We are a certified CertainTeed ShingleMaster contractor, and every one of our installers has completed the CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator exam, to ensure that every job is done to the highest standard possible. We take great pride in doing just a bit more than the standard â€“ we know it makes a difference in the long run. We stand behind our work. Every roof comes with a 10 year workmanship warranty."
